<@U026PHQ3J> and <@U0289USNA> If for some reason you need to get at the awarded_badges or user_badges properties on a badge use the methods userBadgeTypeForCurrentUser and currentUserAwardedBadges on VRMBadge. These filter out user badge types and user awarded badges that may be associated with other users
:thumbsup:
